### DentFlow Appointments API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5199
### All endpoints require Authorization header (JWT Bearer token)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199/api/v1
@authToken = Bearer REPLACE_WITH_VALID_JWT

### ✅ Happy path — Book appointment (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "patientId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "providerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "appointmentTypeId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "startTime": "2026-04-01T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-01T09:30:00Z",
  "notes": "Regular checkup"
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Get appointment by ID (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — List appointments (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Confirm appointment (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/confirm
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Cancel appointment (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "cancellationReason": "Patient requested reschedule"
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Complete appointment (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/complete
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ❌ Validation error — Book appointment with missing required fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "patientId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### 🔒 Unauthorized — No token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments

###

### 🔍 Not found — Get non-existent appointment (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

